      <iTunesMetadata xmlns="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal">
        <translations>
          <translation type="subtitle" xml:lang="en">
            <text for="L1">The bowstring strains, bursting flame that freezes the night sky</text>
            <text for="L2">A cold blue elegy of parting, shooting down the lover...</text>
            <text for="L3">A thing forgotten from distant days, the scars left torn asunder</text>
            <text for="L4">The accursed vow harbored deep within that heart</text>
            <text for="L5">&quot;The inescapable ending — at least let it come by your beloved hand...&quot;</text>
            <text for="L6">The darkness of irresistible impulse enveloped him...</text>
            <text for="L7">A warped world, spiral flames piercing through the cycle of rebirth</text>
            <text for="L8">A cold crimson kiss stained with blood, shooting down the lover...</text>
            <text for="L9">Is there nothing you have left behind...?</text>
            <text for="L10">In an ancient legend: one who is wounded by that demon</text>
            <text for="L11">The curse courses through their entire body</text>
            <text for="L12">And before long shall become the very same demon...</text>
            <text for="L13">When was that wound inflicted?</text>
            <text for="L14">It traces back to the day the two first met</text>
            <text for="L15">The wound he sustained when he saved her</text>
            <text for="L16">Everything had begun from the moment they met...</text>
            <text for="L17">Their meeting was a promise of loss...</text>
            <text for="L18">Tears long withered harbor a sorrowful blue flame</text>
            <text for="L19">Loosing an arrow that gleams with silver light</text>
            <text for="L20">Again and again, only... until he draws his final breath...</text>
            <text for="L21">In a world that has lost its beloved one <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(Why...)</span></text>
            <text for="L22">What color flowers shall ever bloom?</text>
            <text for="L23">A cruciform flame embracing the moon, wound endlessly with briars</text>
            <text for="L24">A cold white arrow of the final hour, shooting me down...</text>
            <text for="L25">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text>
            <text for="L26">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text>
            <text for="L27">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text>
            <text for="L28">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text>
            <text for="L29">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text>
            <text for="L30">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text>
            <text for="L31">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text>
            <text for="L32">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text>
          </translation>
          <translation type="subtitle" xml:lang="zh-Hans">
            <text for="L1">长弓震颤 迸裂的焰火 将夜空凝结</text>
            <text for="L2">凛然苍蓝的诀别之诗 将身为恋人的你射杀……</text>
            <text for="L3">遥远之日的遗留之物 被撕裂的道道伤痕</text>
            <text for="L4">将受诅咒的约定 刻入那胸膛之中</text>
            <text for="L5">「无法逃避的结局 至少由那心爱之人亲手……」</text>
            <text for="L6">无法抗拒的疯狂冲动 将他笼罩吞噬……</text>
            <text for="L7">扭曲世界的螺旋之焰 贯穿轮回往复</text>
            <text for="L8">凛然绯红的血濡之吻 将身为恋人的你射杀……</text>
            <text for="L9">还有什么忘记了吗？……</text>
            <text for="L10">古老的传说中 被那魔物所伤之人</text>
            <text for="L11">诅咒将于全身游走奔涌</text>
            <text for="L12">终有一日 会化作同样的魔物吧…</text>
            <text for="L13">那伤痕又是什么时候留下的？</text>
            <text for="L14">那要追溯至二人相遇的那一天</text>
            <text for="L15">那是他为救她时所受的伤</text>
            <text for="L16">一切自相遇之时 便已悄然开始……</text>
            <text for="L17">相遇即是通往相离的约定……</text>
            <text for="L18">干涸殆尽的泪水 宿有悲伤的苍蓝之焰</text>
            <text for="L19">射出闪耀银色光辉的箭矢</text>
            <text for="L20">无论多少次 直至……他气绝而亡……</text>
            <text for="L21">在失去所爱之人的世界里 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(怎么会……)</span></text>
            <text for="L22">会绽放何种色彩的花呢？</text>
            <text for="L23">环抱月华的十字之焰 荆棘缠绕不倦</text>
            <text for="L24">凛然纯白的临终箭矢 将身为恋人的我射杀……</text>
            <text for="L25">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text>
            <text for="L26">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text>
            <text for="L27">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text>
            <text for="L28">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text>
            <text for="L29">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text>
            <text for="L30">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text>
            <text for="L31">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text>
            <text for="L32">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text>
          </translation>
        </translations>
